  "text": "We chose sputtering as a deposition method as it is inexpensive and routinely used in Si CMOS fabrication for deposition lms over larger areas. While, reports on (111) and (100) textured YSZ lms on Si substrates by controlling various growth parameters such as growth rate, [CITATION_1] growth temperature,",
